Balancer - Open Model:
a2enmod
proxy proxy_ajp proxy_http rewrite deflate headers proxy_balancer proxy_connect proxy_html lbmethod_byrequest

Server - Install PHP5:
sudo apt-get install libapache2-mod-php5

